made this in python by creating the own virtual environment 

steps below!
1. first creat your own virtual environment
command:
python -m venv {name of your virtual environment}
Ex= python -m venv cowWillSay

2. then activate the virtual environment
command:
{name of your virtual environment}\Scripts\activate
Ex - cowWillSay\Scripts\activate

if it shows error that the access is unauthorized then run this command
command:
Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned

after this repeat step 2 until the virtual environment is not opened

3. Now download the cowsay package
command:
pip install cowsay

4. create a new python file in that environment
Ex- test.py

5. write this code
code:
import cowsay

cowsay.cow("{Your Message}")

6.Run test.py











